title: Arbor Skateboards :: 2015 Product Profiles - Jasper and the Backlash 37
description:
The Backlash 37 is a downhill design with a true kicktail dedicated to smaller riders. It features rocker that runs between the trucks, a snub nose design, and flush routed truck mounts to maintain turning angle while providing superior slide control. No limits - bomb, flip, slide - whatever. 

L: 37.00" W: 9.50" WB: 22.00" - 23.50"

To learn more about the Backlash 37 visit: http://arborcollective.com/skateboard.

Rider: Jasper Ohlson
Film/Edit: Jack Boston
